description: "Admin sayfaları scaffold (list, create, edit). @new-page ile referans verip entity adını kebab-case belirt."
alwaysApply: false
---

Verilen entity için admin panel sayfalarını scaffold et.

## Adımlar

1. Entity adlarını türet: `entity-name` (kebab), `EntityName` (Pascal)
2. Referans oku: `src/app/(baseLayout)/mail-accounts/` altındaki page'ler

3. **List page**: `src/app/(baseLayout)/{entity-name}/page.tsx`
   - `'use client'` directive
   - `use{EntityName}` hook'tan `listQuery`
   - `DataTable` with column definitions
   - Delete confirmation via `AlertDialog`
   - Link to `/new` ve `/[id]/edit`
   - Loading spinner, error toast, empty state
   - Breadcrumb: Dashboard > {Entity Name}

4. **Create page**: `src/app/(baseLayout)/{entity-name}/new/page.tsx`
   - `'use client'` directive
   - React Hook Form + Zod schema
   - `createMutation` from hook
   - Success toast + redirect to list
   - Breadcrumb: Dashboard > {Entity Name} > Yeni

5. **Edit page**: `src/app/(baseLayout)/{entity-name}/[id]/edit/page.tsx`
   - `'use client'` directive
   - `useParams()` to get `id`
   - `getQuery(id)` to fetch existing data
   - React Hook Form with `defaultValues`
   - `updateMutation` from hook
   - Loading state while fetching
   - Breadcrumb: Dashboard > {Entity Name} > Düzenle

6. Raporda hatırlat:
   - Sidebar menu entry: `src/app/_components/Sidebar.tsx`
   - Zod schema yoksa: `@new-service` veya `/new-service` ile oluştur
